References
==========

MathJax
-------

Beautiful math in all browsers, with javascript.
http://www.mathjax.org/


Correct Justification
---------------------

Correct justification with hyphens.
http://www.quirksmode.org/oddsandends/wbr.html

   * wbr-tag  (hyphenless)
   * &shy;  (adds hyphens if needed)

Inject the word breaks with javascript.
http://ejohn.org/blog/injecting-word-breaks-with-javascript/


